com.kamontat.constants

Enum SizeUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SizeUnit>
      • com.kamontat.constants.SizeUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SizeUnit>

    public enum SizeUnit
extends Enum<SizeUnit>
    contains the unit of file size and type of that unit
    The type we have 2 type
    1. SI - SizeUnitType.SI
    2. Non-SI - SizeUnitType.NON_SI
    Since:
    Thu 16/Mar/2017 - 12:02 AM
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    kamontat
    See Also:
    SizeUnitType

      • to

        public BigDecimal to(BigDecimal number,
                     int decimalPoint,
                     SizeUnit unit)
        convert this unit to any unit that you pass from the parameter
        and return the decimal number in decimal point number
        Example: decimalPoint=2
        the return value will compute until 2 number after pass dot (##.XX)
        Parameters:
        number - the conversion number
        decimalPoint - the number of number after dot (###.XX)
        unit - the unit that want to convert to
        Returns:
        number that already converted
